*kde-3.1.1 (14 Mar 2003)

  14 Mar 2003; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> kde-3.1.1.ebuild:
  A security patch release fixing a kghostview vulnerability. See GLSA.
  Also includes misc other fixes.

*kde-3.1 (01 Feb 2003)

  28 Feb 2003; Will Woods <wwoods@gentoo.org> kde-3.1.ebuild:
  Added ~alpha to keywords

  12 Feb 2003; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> kde-3.0.2.ebuild,
  kde-3.0.3.ebuild, kde-3.0.3a.ebuild, kde-3.1_rc6.ebuild: removed
  old versions

*kde-3.1_rc6 (05 Jan 2003)

  15 Feb 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> kde-3.1.ebuild:
  Changed ~sparc keyword to sparc.

  01 Feb 2003; Jack Morgan <jmorgan@gentoo.org> kde-3.1.ebuild:
  added ~sparc to keywords

  08 Jan 2003; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> kde-3.1_rc6.ebuild:
  added ~ppc to keywords

  05 Jan 2003; Hannes Mehnert <hannes@gentoo.org> kde-3.1_rc6.ebuild:
  version bump

*kde-3.0.5a (21 Dec 2003)

  06 Jan 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> kde-3.0.5a.ebuild:
